channel.title: Aliana Lohan - Long Way Down (Kamal Remix)
channel.description:
https://soundcloud.com/kamal-givens/long-way-down/s-naIcn
This is an old song by Aliana Lohan, the acappella was sent to me and I cut the vocals into 8bar sections to fit it onto auxy. The whole instrumental was done on auxy. I held back on posting this though, due to hearing about that guy stealing peoples music and putting it onto Spotify, as his own music.
